snippet.title: v3.8 [Dawn of Glory] Trailer - Honkai Impact 3
snippet.description:
The World Serpent has revealed its fangs and Schicksal has aimed its lance. The arrival of Schicksal's strongest Valkyrie announces the end remains uncertain.
HI3 v3.8 [Dawn of Glory] coming soon! Durandal's A-rank battlesuit [Valkyrie Gloria] and Story Chapter XV [The Prodigal Girl Returns] await!
